                    <p>Use class <code>.sortable</code> to <code>.list-group</code> for sortable list group.</p>
                    <ul class="list-group sortable">
                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center"><span class="mr-2"><i class="fas fa-sort text-muted mr-2"></i>0.1</span> Cras justo odio</li>
