                    </ul>
                    <hr>
                    {{{card_title 'Themed'}}}
                    <p>Use contextual classes <code>.list-group-item-*</code> to style list items with a stateful background and color.</p>
                    <ul class="list-group sortable">
                        <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-primary d-flex align-items-center"><span class="mr-2"><i class="fas fa-sort text-muted mr-2"></i>0.1</span> Cras justo odio</li>
